Shipping Info

Name:

{user.name}

Phone:

{shippingInfo.phoneNo}

Address:

{address}
Your Crat Items:
{cartItems && cartItems.map((item) =>(
{item.name} {""} {item.quantity} X ₹{item.price} = {""} ₹{item.price * item.quantity }
))}
{/* */}
Order Summary

Subtotal:

₹{subtotal}

Shipping Charges:

₹{shippingCharges}

GST:

₹{tax}

Total:

₹{totalPrice}
); }; export default ConfirmOrder;
